    "body": [
      "Our conference has been held for two years in the Balkan region, in Serbia and Montenegro.",
      "Previously, our agency, Lead Volume, organized blockchain and digital marketing events in Turkey, Kazakhstan, Serbia, Montenegro and Russia.",
      "Our team has held over 20 conferences in five countries over the past 10 years.",
      "BWiGA brings together participants from more than 30 countries, including guests from Cyprus, England, India, Turkey, Hungary, Georgia, Ukraine, Germany, Bulgaria, Russia, Norway, Croatia, the Czech Republic, Latvia, and many others.",
      "BWiGA has become a landmark event for the region in the web3 and iGaming industries, focusing on awards for the best projects and industry figures. This unique event is covered by media outlets such as Business Insider, Benzinga, and CoinMarketCap.",
      "BWiGA typically awards over 30 winners per event, and this competition features over 100 nominees from around the world!"
    ],
